:false,"followUpAction":"suggest_send_message","cooldownSeconds":400,"requiredMoods":[],"minAttentionDrain":10,"maxAttentionDrain":10,"audioFilename":null,"audioUrl":null},{"id":"light_01","category":"idle","tone":"playful","lineText":"You are settling in. That is good. This is a comfortable place to browse.","v3Text":null,"usesV3":false,"followUpAction":null,"cooldownSeconds":120,"requiredMoods":[],"minAttentionDrain":3,"maxAttentionDrain":5,"audioFilename":null,"audioUrl":null},{"id":"light_02","category":"flirty","tone":"seductive","lineText":"Take a good listen. The right voice has a way of stopping you mid-skip.","v3Text":null,"usesV3":false,"followUpAction":null,"cooldownSeconds":140,"requiredMoods":[],"minAttentionDrain":3,"maxAttentionDrain":5,"audioFilename":null,"audioUrl":null},{"id":"light_03","category":"idle","tone":"comedic","lineText":"Still here. Good. I like the company.","v3Text":null,"usesV3":false,"followUpAction":null,"cooldownSeconds":120,"requiredMoods":[],"minAttentionDrain":3,"maxAttentionDrain":5,"audioFilename":null,"audioUrl":null},{"id":"light_04","category":"flirty","tone":"playful","lineText":"Each skip is a choice. You know your taste better than you think.","v3Text":null,"usesV3":false,"followUpAction":null,"cooldownSeconds":130,"requiredMoods":[],"minAttentionDrain":3,"maxAttentionDrain":5,"audioFilename":null,"audioUrl":null},{"id":"light_05","category":"idle","tone":"seductive","lineText":"No rush on my end. Stay as long as you need.","v3Text":null,"usesV3":false,"followUpAction":null,"cooldownSeconds":120,"requiredMoods":[],"minAttentionDrain":3,"maxAttentionDrain":5,"audioFilename":null,"audioUrl":null},{"id":"light_06","category":"flirty","tone":"teasing","lineText":"A few skips in. Still hunting. That is the spirit.","v3Text":null,"usesV3":false,"followUpAction":null,"cooldownSeconds":130,"requiredMoods":[],"minAttentionDrain":3,"maxAttentionDrain":5,"audioFilename":null,"audioUrl":null},{"id":"light_07","category":"idle","tone":"playful","lineText":"Sometimes it takes a minute to tune in. You are doing just fine.","v3Text":null,"usesV3":false,"followUpAction":null,"cooldownSeconds":120,"requiredMoods":[],"minAttentionDrain":3,"maxAttentionDrain":5,"audioFilename":null,"audioUrl":null},{"id":"light_08","category":"reengagement","tone":"playful","lineText":"You are building up a picture of what you want. That is actually a smart way to browse.","v3Text":null,"usesV3":false,"followUpAction":null,"cooldownSeconds":160,"requiredMoods":[],"minAttentionDrain":3,"maxAttentionDrain":5,"audioFilename":null,"audioUrl":null},{"id":"medium_01","category":"picky","tone":"teasing","lineText":"Seven skips and counting. Your standards are doing the heavy lifting right now.","v3Text":null,"usesV3":false,"followUpAction":null,"cooldownSeconds":200,"requiredMoods":[],"minAttentionDrain":5,"maxAttentionDrain":7,"audioFilename":null,"audioUrl":null},{"id":"medium_02","category":"reengagement","tone":"playful","lineText":"Two minutes in. Still nothing sent. You are warming up. That is fine. But eventually the warmup has to end.","v3Text":null,"usesV3":false,"followUpAction":"suggest_send_message","cooldownSeconds":220,"requiredMoods":[],"minAttentionDrain":5,"maxAttentionDrain":7,"audioFilename":null,"audioUrl":null},{"id":"medium_03","category":"idle","tone":"comedic","lineText":"You have been here a hot minute without doing much. Not judging. But also a little judging.","v3Text":null,"usesV3":false,"followUpAction":null,"cooldownSeconds":180,"requiredMoods":[],"minAttentionDrain":5,"maxAttentionDrain":7,"audioFilename":null,"audioUrl":null},{"id":"medium_04","category":"flirty","tone":"seductive","lineText":"Whoever you are looking for — he is probably somewhere in this line. You just have to get to him.","v3Text":null,"usesV3":false,"followUpAction":"suggest_send_message","cooldownSeconds":200,"requiredMoods":[],"minAttentionDrain":5,"maxAttentionDrain":7,"audioFilename":null,"audioUrl":null},{"id":"medium_05","category":"picky","tone":"comedic","lineText":"Nine guys in the skip pile. You could start a whole rejected caller support group at this point.","v3Text":null,"usesV3":false,"followUpAction":null,"cooldownSeconds":240,"requiredMoods":[],"minAttentionDrain":5,"maxAttentionDrain":7,"audioFilename":null,"audioUrl":null},{"id":"medium_06","category":"reengagement","tone":"teasing","lineText":"Three minutes and no messages. The guys out there are starting to wonder if you are even real.","v3Text":null,"usesV3":false,"followUpAction":"suggest_send_message","cooldownSeconds":240,"requiredMoods":[],"minAttentionDrain":6,"maxAttentionDrain":7,"audioFilename":null,"audioUrl":null},{"id":"medium_07","category":"flirty","tone":"playful","lineText":"You know what they say — the right voice hits differently. You are close. Keep going.","v3Text":null,"usesV3":false,"followUpAction":null,"cooldownSeconds":200,"requiredMoods":[],"minAttentionDrain":5,"maxAttentionDrain":7,"audioFilename":null,"audioUrl":null},{"id":"medium_08","category":"idle","tone":"teasing","lineText":"You are in a listening mood right now. Nothing wrong with that. But listening only gets you so far.","v3Text":null,"usesV3":false,"followUpAction":"suggest_send_message","cooldownSeconds":200,"requiredMoods":[],"minAttentionDrain":5,"maxAttentionDrain":7,"audioFilename":null,"audioUrl":null},{"id":"reward_extra_01","category":"reward","tone":"playful","lineText":"You sent a message. That took about two seconds and it was absolutely the right call.","v3Text":null,"usesV3":false,"followUpAction":null,"cooldownSeconds":280,"requiredMoods":[],"minAttentionDrain":3,"maxAttentionDrain":10,"audioFilename":null,"audioUrl":null},{"id":"reward_extra_02","category":"reward","tone":"seductive","lineText":"Two messages in. You are officially the most interesting person on this line right now.","v3Text":null,"usesV3":false,"followUpAction":null,"cooldownSeconds":320,"requiredMoods":[],"minAttentionDrain":3,"maxAttentionDrain":10,"audioFilename":null,"audioUrl":null},{"id":"reward_extra_03","category":"reward","tone":"comedic","lineText":"There it is. First message out. That is how you do it.","v3Text":null,"usesV3":false,"followUpAction":null,"cooldownSeconds":260,"requiredMoods":[],"minAttentionDrain":3,"maxAttentionDrain":10,"audioFilename":null,"audioUrl":null},{"id":"reward_extra_04","category":"reward","tone":"teasing","lineText":"Three messages? You are not here to browse. You are here to connect. I see you.","v3Text":null,"usesV3":false,"followUpAction":null,"cooldownSeconds":360,"requiredMoods":[],"minAttentionDrain":3,"maxAttentionDrain":10,"audioFilename":null,"audioUrl":null},{"id":"reward_extra_05","category":"reward","tone":"seductive","lineText":"Every message you send is a chance at something real. You are playing this perfectly.","v3Text":null,"usesV3":false,"followUpAction":null,"cooldownSeconds":300,"requiredMoods":[],"minAttentionDrain":3,"maxAttentionDrain":10,"audioFilename":null,"audioUrl":null},{"id":"roger_01","category":"idle","tone":"comedic","lineText":"Just so you know, Roger is watching. Not in a weird way. In a supportive way.","v3Text":null,"usesV3":false,"followUpAction":null,"cooldownSeconds":160,"requiredMoods":[],"minAttentionDrain":3,"maxAttentionDrain":10,"audioFilename":null,"audioUrl":null},{"id":"roger_02","category":"picky","tone":"comedic","lineText":"You know how they say all the good ones are taken? They are not. They are right here on this line.","v3Text":null,"usesV3":false,"followUpAction":"suggest_send_message","cooldownSeconds":200,"requiredMoods":[],"minAttentionDrain":4,"maxAttentionDrain":10,"audioFilename":null,"audioUrl":null},{"id":"roger_03","category":"flirty","tone":"comedic","lineText":"What if I told you the next profile is exactly your type? You'll never know unless you listen.","v3Text":null,"usesV3":false,"followUpAction":null,"cooldownSeconds":180,"requiredMoods":[],"minAttentionDrain":4,"maxAttentionDrain":10,"audioFilename":null,"audioUrl":null},{"id":"roger_04","category":"idle","tone":"comedic","lineText":"You have been very still. Which means either you are very relaxed or you are overthinking everything. Either way — say hello to someone.","v3Text":"[sighs] You have been very still. [curious] Which means either you are very relaxed or you are overthinking everything. [warmly] Either way — say hello to someone.","usesV3":true,"followUpAction":"suggest_send_message","cooldownSeconds":200,"requiredMoods":[],"minAttentionDrain":5,"maxAttentionDrain":10,"audioFilename":null,"audioUrl":null},{"id":"roger_05","category":"picky","tone":"comedic","lineText":"Eleven skips. I have started giving them all nicknames. Skip. Skipped. Also Skipped. Another Skip.","v3Text":"[chuckles] Eleven skips. [deadpan] I have started giving them all nicknames. Skip. Skipped. Also Skipped. Another Skip.","usesV3":true,"followUpAction":null,"cooldownSeconds":260,"requiredMoods":[],"minAttentionDrain":6,"maxAttentionDrain":10,"audioFilename":null,"audioUrl":null},{"id":"roger_06","category":"reengagement","tone":"comedic","lineText":"You know what I have never heard anyone regret? Sending a message. Just something to think about.","v3Text":"[warmly] You know what I have never heard anyone regret? [playfully] Sending a message. Just something to think about.","usesV3":true,"followUpAction":"suggest_send_message","cooldownSeconds":260,"requiredMoods":[],"minAttentionDrain":6,"maxAttentionDrain":10,"audioFilename":null,"audioUrl":null},{"id":"roger_07","category":"flirty","tone":"comedic","lineText":"Somewhere on this line is a guy who would absolutely love to get a message from you. He just does not know it yet.","v3Text":"[mischievously] Somewhere on this line is a guy who would absolutely love to get a message from you. [whispers] He just does not know it yet.","usesV3":true,"followUpAction":"suggest_send_message","cooldownSeconds":200,"requiredMoods":[],"minAttentionDrain":4,"maxAttentionDrain":10,"audioFilename":null,"audioUrl":null},{"id":"roger_08","category":"dominant","tone":"comedic","lineText":"At some point browsing stops being productive and starts being an avoidance strategy. You might be there. Send a message.","v3Text":null,"usesV3":false,"followUpAction":"suggest_send_message","cooldownSeconds":300,"requiredMoods":[],"minAttentionDrain":7,"maxAttentionDrain":10,"audioFilename":null,"audioUrl":null}]
